Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:04.92,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}Somewhere in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:09.49,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}I hear joy in a song I'll never know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:16.01,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}This curse, I can't take it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.31,0:24:21.37,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}I pray for the dying everglow
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:26.73,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}You know I can't wither away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:32.24,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}Over the shadows deliverance awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.24,0:24:38.93,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}Time is still racing like a river, day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:51.62,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}果てしない世界へ　暗闇を駆け抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.62,0:24:57.05,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}Just trying to find a place where I belong
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.05,0:25:01.32,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}I know it's somewhere out there, our heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:04.62,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}The flame within will burn forever
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.62,0:25:09.74,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}帳はもうないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:15.80,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}寄る辺ない暗闇の星たちを数えて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:20.92,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}灯火を掲げて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.92,0:25:28.30,ed-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}あの遥かなる地へ　今は生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.76,0:24:04.92,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}在遙遠之地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:09.49,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}我沉浸於從未聽過的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:16.01,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}我無法承受這詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.31,0:24:21.37,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}為即將消逝的光芒祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.62,0:24:26.73,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}我還不能毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:32.24,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}仍有陰影待我拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.24,0:24:38.93,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}時間依舊如河水般流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:51.62,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}衝破黑暗 奔向無垠的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.62,0:24:57.05,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}我只想尋找歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.05,0:25:01.32,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}我知道我們的樂土不在此處
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:04.62,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}心中火焰永不熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.62,0:25:09.74,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}帷帳已不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.74,0:25:15.80,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}細數黑暗中的孤星
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:20.92,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}高舉手中燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.92,0:25:28.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)}為前往那遙遠之地 生存下去
